---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import LessonNav from '../../components/LessonNav.astro';
---
<Layout title="Lesson 1.03 — Design Process Documentation">
  <span class="lesson-badge">Lesson 1.03</span>
  <h1>Design Process Documentation</h1>
  
  <p>
    The <strong>design process</strong> section is typically one of the highest-weighted parts of the 
    Engineering Portfolio. This lesson covers how to document your team's journey from problem to solution.
  </p>

  <h2>The Engineering Design Process</h2>
  <p>Most judges expect you to demonstrate a structured approach to problem-solving:</p>
  
  <div class="process-steps">
    <div class="step">
      <span class="step-num">1</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Define</strong>
        <p>What problem are you solving?</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <span class="step-num">2</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Research</strong>
        <p>What solutions already exist?</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <span class="step-num">3</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Brainstorm</strong>
        <p>Generate multiple ideas</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <span class="step-num">4</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Prototype</strong>
        <p>Build quick models—either online or physical</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <span class="step-num">5</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Test</strong>
        <p>Gather data, evaluate options</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <span class="step-num">6</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Iterate</strong>
        <p>Improve based on results</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Problem Definition</h2>
  <p>Start by clearly stating the challenge you're addressing:</p>
  
  <blockquote>
    Our robot needs to lift game elements 24 inches high while staying within the 18" starting size constraint.
  </blockquote>

  <p>Include:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Game requirements</li>
    <li>Constraints (size, weight, rules)</li>
    <li>Success criteria</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Decision Matrix</h2>
  <p>Document multiple design ideas, not just the final one. Create a decision matrix to compare options:</p>
  
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Concept</th>
        <th>Simplicity</th>
        <th>Reliability</th>
        <th>Speed</th>
        <th>Total</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Linear slide</td>
        <td>8</td>
        <td>9</td>
        <td>7</td>
        <td><strong>24/30</strong></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Scissor lift</td>
        <td>6</td>
        <td>7</td>
        <td>9</td>
        <td><strong>22/30</strong></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Arm mechanism</td>
        <td>7</td>
        <td>8</td>
        <td>8</td>
        <td><strong>23/30</strong></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Document Your Iterations</h2>
  <p>Show your iterative process with each version:</p>
  
  <div class="iteration-cards">
    <div class="iteration">
      <span class="iter-label">v1</span>
      <h4>First Prototype</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>What you built</li>
        <li>What you tested</li>
        <li>Problems encountered</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="iteration">
      <span class="iter-label">v2</span>
      <h4>Second Iteration</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Changes made</li>
        <li>New test results</li>
        <li>Improvements observed</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="iteration">
      <span class="iter-label">v3</span>
      <h4>Final Design</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Final refinements</li>
        <li>Performance metrics</li>
        <li>Why you're confident</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="callout tip">
    <strong><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: -0.15em; margin-right: 0.25em;"><path d="M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5"></path><path d="M9 18h6"></path><path d="M10 22h4"></path></svg>Data is King:</strong> Use quantitative data whenever possible. Instead of 
    "The intake worked well," write "The intake had an 80% success rate with an average cycle time of 2.3 seconds."
  </div>

  <LessonNav 
    prev={{ title: "Best Practices", href: "/lessons/lesson-2/" }}
    next={{ title: "CAD & Drawings", href: "/lessons/lesson-4/" }}
  />
</Layout>

<style>
  .lesson-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.35rem 0.75rem;
    background: var(--accent-faint);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  h1 {
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .process-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: var(--bg-surface-solid);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .step-num {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .step strong {
    display: block;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
  }

  .step p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .iteration-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .iteration {
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: var(--bg-surface-solid);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .iter-label {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    background: var(--accent-faint);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .iteration h4 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-heading);
  }

  .iteration ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .callout {
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .callout.tip {
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.08);
    border-left: 3px solid #10b981;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  [data-theme="dark"] .callout.tip {
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.12);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .process-steps {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
    
    .iteration-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .process-steps {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
